abstract: |
  A configuration, benchmarking, and tooling repo for running Qwen3.5 GGUF models
  locally with llama.cpp on 16GB NVIDIA GPUs. It includes reproducible launcher
  presets, benchmark artifacts, multimodal request helpers, and technical notes
  around the observed 35B context-performance cliff on the primary RTX 5080 test
  machine.
